.TH DFM 1
.SH NAME
dfm \- Dotfiles manager and install helper
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdfm\fR [COMMAND]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Dotfiles manager and install helper
.PP
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
\fBinstall\fR
Install tools, packages, and configurations
.TP
\fBinstall all\fR
Install everything in the correct order
.TP
\fBinstall apt\-packages\fR
Install apt packages (Debian/Ubuntu)
.TP
\fBinstall cheat\-databases\fR
Install cheat external cheatsheet databases
.TP
\fBinstall composer\fR
Install PHP Package Manager Composer
.TP
\fBinstall dnf\-packages\fR
Install dnf packages (Fedora/RHEL)
.TP
\fBinstall fonts\fR
Install programming fonts
.TP
\fBinstall gh\fR
Install GitHub CLI Extensions
.TP
\fBinstall git\-crypt\fR
Install git\-crypt from source
.TP
\fBinstall imagick\fR
Install ImageMagick CLI
.TP
\fBinstall macos\fR
Setup nice macOS defaults
.TP
\fBinstall mise\fR
Install tools via mise (runtimes + CLI tools)
.TP
\fBinstall mise\-cleanup\fR
Remove old version manager installations
.TP
\fBinstall ntfy\fR
Install ntfy notification tool
.TP
\fBinstall python\-libs\fR
Install Python libraries (libtmux, pynvim)
.TP
\fBinstall shellspec\fR
Install shellspec testing framework
.TP
\fBinstall xcode\-cli\-tools\fR
Install Xcode CLI tools (macOS)
.TP
\fBinstall z\fR
Install z directory jumper
.TP
\fBbrew\fR
Homebrew package management
.TP
\fBbrew install\fR
Install packages from Brewfile
.TP
\fBbrew update\fR
Update Homebrew and packages
.TP
\fBbrew updatebundle\fR
Update Brewfile with descriptions
.TP
\fBbrew autoupdate\fR
Setup Homebrew auto\-update
.TP
\fBbrew leaves\fR
List installed\-on\-request packages
.TP
\fBbrew clean\fR
Cleanup old versions
.TP
\fBbrew untracked\fR
List packages not in Brewfile
.TP
\fBapt\fR
APT package management (Debian/Ubuntu)
.TP
\fBapt upkeep\fR
Full maintenance (update + upgrade + autoremove + clean)
.TP
\fBapt install\fR
Install packages from apt.txt
.TP
\fBapt update\fR
Update package lists
.TP
\fBapt upgrade\fR
Upgrade installed packages
.TP
\fBapt autoremove\fR
Remove unused packages
.TP
\fBapt clean\fR
Clean package cache
.TP
\fBcheck\fR
System information checks
.TP
\fBcheck arch\fR
Get or check current architecture
.RS
\fIAliases: \fRa
.RE
.TP
\fBcheck host\fR
Get or check current hostname
.RS
\fIAliases: \fRh, hostname
.RE
.TP
\fBdotfiles\fR
Format and reset configurations
.TP
\fBdotfiles fmt\fR
Run all formatters
.TP
\fBdotfiles yamlfmt\fR
Format YAML files
.TP
\fBdotfiles shfmt\fR
Format shell scripts
.TP
\fBdotfiles reset_all\fR
Reset everything
.TP
\fBdotfiles reset_nvim\fR
Reset neovim state and config
.TP
\fBhelpers\fR
Display system information
.TP
\fBhelpers aliases\fR
Show shell aliases
.TP
\fBhelpers colors\fR
Show 256 terminal colors
.TP
\fBhelpers env\fR
Show environment variables
.TP
\fBhelpers functions\fR
Show shell functions
.TP
\fBhelpers nvim\fR
Show neovim keybindings
.TP
\fBhelpers path\fR
Show PATH directories
.TP
\fBhelpers tmux\fR
Show tmux keybindings
.TP
\fBhelpers wezterm\fR
Show wezterm keybindings
.TP
\fBdocs\fR
Generate documentation
.TP
\fBdocs all\fR
Update all keybindings docs
.TP
\fBdocs tmux\fR
Update tmux keybindings
.TP
\fBdocs nvim\fR
Update nvim keybindings
.TP
\fBdocs wezterm\fR
Update wezterm keybindings
.TP
\fBscripts\fR
Run install scripts from scripts/
.TP
\fBtests\fR
Test visualization helpers
.TP
\fBtests msgr\fR
Show all msgr message types
.TP
\fBtests params\fR
List all parameters
.TP
\fBhelp\fR
Show help
.SH "DFM INSTALL MISE-CLEANUP"
Remove old version manager installations
.PP
\fBUsage:\fR dfm install mise\-cleanup [OPTIONS]
.PP
\fBOptions:\fR
.PP
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Show what would be removed without removing
.SH "DFM CHECK ARCH"
Get or check current architecture
.PP
\fBUsage:\fR dfm check arch [<arch>]
.PP
\fBArguments:\fR
.PP
.TP
\fB<arch>\fR
Architecture to check against
.SH "DFM CHECK HOST"
Get or check current hostname
.PP
\fBUsage:\fR dfm check host [<hostname>]
.PP
\fBArguments:\fR
.PP
.TP
\fB<hostname>\fR
Hostname to check against
.SH "DFM HELPERS ALIASES"
Show shell aliases
.PP
\fBUsage:\fR dfm helpers aliases <shell>
.PP
\fBArguments:\fR
.PP
.TP
\fB<shell>\fR
Shell to show aliases for (bash, zsh, fish)
.SH "DFM SCRIPTS"
Run install scripts from scripts/
.PP
\fBUsage:\fR dfm scripts [<script>]
.PP
\fBArguments:\fR
.PP
.TP
\fB<script>\fR
Script name to run (without install\- prefix)
.SH AUTHOR
Ismo Vuorinen
